data.meta_description: PrepMe.US | 15 followers on LinkedIn. Prep Me is a digital roadmap that streamlines the college application process | Prep Me is a digital roadmap that streamlines the college application process making it possible to focus on writing applications instead of chasing deadlines. Prep Me efficiently manages all aspects of the college application process: essays, transcripts, letters of recommendation, and testing, all without the steep costs of consultants or long lines at the school resource center. By instantly generating a personalized plan to guide students through each step of all their applications, we provide students access to resources they never knew they needed, including webinars with admissions officers, proven test prep courses, and personalized admissions predictions.
